  "detailed_description": "<h1>Just Updated</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/1affbf7cc7d7fbe509daa7704560e4f9.poster.avif?t=1766480922\" width=616 height=2580 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/1affbf7cc7d7fbe509daa7704560e4f9.webm?t=1766480922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/1affbf7cc7d7fbe509daa7704560e4f9.mp4?t=1766480922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armored Warfare is a free-to-play MMO with story-driven elements where you can engage in explosive online tank battles against players around the world or team up to defeat AI-controlled enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/0861205bcadc4db411cbab0aac88fab5.poster.avif?t=1766480922\" width=616 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/0861205bcadc4db411cbab0aac88fab5.webm?t=1766480922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/0861205bcadc4db411cbab0aac88fab5.mp4?t=1766480922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a soldier of fortune and complete missions, from simple capture and escort objectives to complex story-driven PvE campaigns. Armored Warfare features deep, immersive lore where corporations rule the world, hiring mercenary groups such as yours to wage war. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/ef6c453a9f9c4cfef75e79c0d71ab925.poster.avif?t=1766480922\" width=616 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/ef6c453a9f9c4cfef75e79c0d71ab925.webm?t=1766480922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/ef6c453a9f9c4cfef75e79c0d71ab925.mp4?t=1766480922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armored Warfare features large-scale battlefields full of armored vehicles and infantry, from massive 15 versus 15 PvP matches to smaller 5-man operations. Armored Warfare does have something for everybody.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/d9d03823f6402fc2e0513acddc642e71.poster.avif?t=1766480922\" width=616 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/d9d03823f6402fc2e0513acddc642e71.webm?t=1766480922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/d9d03823f6402fc2e0513acddc642e71.mp4?t=1766480922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control hundreds of modern armored vehicles across several eras, ranging from the 1950s to the 2030s, all meticulously modeled after their real-life counterparts. Five epic classes will satisfy every gameplay style, from heavily armored MBTs, light AFV scouts to Tank Destroyer snipers. Over 34 countries represented, yours likely included! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/7b989d17134f9e27ca70299c8d8743b4.poster.avif?t=1766480922\" width=616 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/7b989d17134f9e27ca70299c8d8743b4.webm?t=1766480922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/7b989d17134f9e27ca70299c8d8743b4.mp4?t=1766480922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Massive clashes with legendary combat moments await you. Lay down torrents of fire or stop an advancing armored company by calling in an air strike. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/4319d3f47b34fb87435271ccac5455d8.poster.avif?t=1766480922\" width=616 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/4319d3f47b34fb87435271ccac5455d8.webm?t=1766480922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/4319d3f47b34fb87435271ccac5455d8.mp4?t=1766480922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Armored Warfare is updated on monthly (or even weekly) basis with regular content drops including new vehicles, maps, events and game modes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/289f7aecc3af5659e04ee014d7c30c42.poster.avif?t=1766480922\" width=616 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/289f7aecc3af5659e04ee014d7c30c42.webm?t=1766480922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/289f7aecc3af5659e04ee014d7c30c42.mp4?t=1766480922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Dozens of maps await you, from scorching African deserts to the mountains of China, Northern tundra, and neon-drenched urban jungles. Who knows where the evolving storyline takes you next? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/b25c3ee25a2d9991170affffa0fefb18.avif?t=1766480922\" width=616 height=92 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armored Warfare is a free-to-play MMO with story-driven elements where you can engage in explosive online tank battles against players around the world or team up to defeat AI-controlled enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/0861205bcadc4db411cbab0aac88fab5.poster.avif?t=1766480922\" width=616 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/0861205bcadc4db411cbab0aac88fab5.webm?t=1766480922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/0861205bcadc4db411cbab0aac88fab5.mp4?t=1766480922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a soldier of fortune and complete missions, from simple capture and escort objectives to complex story-driven PvE campaigns. Armored Warfare features deep, immersive lore where corporations rule the world, hiring mercenary groups such as yours to wage war. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/ef6c453a9f9c4cfef75e79c0d71ab925.poster.avif?t=1766480922\" width=616 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/ef6c453a9f9c4cfef75e79c0d71ab925.webm?t=1766480922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/443110/extras/ef6c453a9f9c4cfef75e79c0d71ab925.mp4?t=1766480922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armored Warfare features large-scale battlefields full of armored vehicles and infantry, from massive 15 versus 15 PvP matches to smalle